Package: actuaRE
Type: Package
Title: Handling Hierarchically Structured Risk Factors using Random
        Effects Models
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: c(person("Campo", "Bavo D.C.", role = c("aut", "cre"),
		     email = "bavo.decock@kuleuven.be"))
Description: Using this package, you can fit a random effects model using either the hierarchical credibility model, a combination of the hierarchical credibility model with a generalized linear model or a Tweedie generalized linear mixed model. See Campo, B.D.C. and Antonio, K. (2022) <arXiv:2206.15244>.
License: GPL (>= 3)
